{{Youmay|the vibrospade, also known as a vibroshovel|the [[power-shovel]]}}
A '''vibrospade''', or '''vibroshovel''', was a digging tool with an internal generator that made the blade vibrate rapidly in the same manner as a [[Vibroblade/Legends|vibroblade]]. This allowed the tool to more easily dig through hard-pack gravel, sand, or dirt.

